short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A GitHub Universe inspired theme for any GitHub pages.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: GitHub Prettify is a theme for github.com.  Any urls that you visit in github will apply the styling of this extension.  The them is based off of the GitHub Universe.
